{"type":"message","id":"d62b6944","parentId":"778292de","timestamp":"2026-03-19T08:50:02.763Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我有什么技能。我可以查看 AGENTS.md 或者直接列出已安装的技能。根据 MEMORY.md 中的记录，已安装的技能包括：\n\n- skill-finder-cn\n- openclaw-tavily-search\n- multi-search-engine\n- office-automation-test\n- cron-mastery\n- news-summary\n- free-ride\n- browser-automation\n- desktop-control-win\n- self-improving\n- proactivity\n- skill-vetter\n- memory-setup\n\n还有一些飞书相关的技能是内置的。让我给用户列出来。","thinkingSignature":"57412e44565bcb90f9d309c3ead62e17413e0f53441332da76504650807ac559"},{"type":"text","text":"Sir 好！我目前有以下技能：\n\n**🔍 搜索类**\n- skill-finder-cn - 技能查找器\n- multi-search-engine - 多引擎搜索（17个搜索引擎）\n- openclaw-tavily-search - Tavily 搜索\n\n**🛠️ 工具类**\n- browser-automation - 浏览器自动化\n- desktop-control-win - Windows 桌面控制\n- cron-mastery - 定时任务管理\n\n**📰 资讯类**\n- news-summary - 新闻汇总\n\n**🧠 进阶类**\n- self-improving - 自我改进（学习纠正）\n- proactivity - 主动工作\n- memory-setup - 记忆配置\n- skill-vetter - 技能安全审查\n\n**�飞书内置**\n- 日历管理、任务管理、多维表格、云文档、消息读取等\n\n有什么想让我帮忙的？🦐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":64,"output":295,"cacheRead":36685,"cacheWrite":846,"totalTokens":37890,"cost":{"input":0.0000192,"output":0.000354,"cacheRead":0.0011005499999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00010151999999999999,"total":0.0015752699999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773910193448}}
