{"type":"message","id":"a7a25699","parentId":"a81542d5","timestamp":"2026-03-19T08:54:45.563Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很好！tushare-data 看起来是一个非常适合国内使用的金融数据接口技能。让我给用户推荐这些技能。","thinkingSignature":"cb3ff84905ede3f9f3f1a8e8b06077bf90dd152563abeb84ab76917c6a28dbf7"},{"type":"text","text":"Sir，找到了不少适合国内使用的金融类技能 🎌\n\n**📊 强烈推荐（已安装）**\n- **tushare-data** - 财经数据接口，支持股票、基金、期货、数字货币等行情数据及基本面数据\n\n**🔍 其他热门选择**\n| 技能名 | 描述 |\n|--------|------|\n| eastmoney-stock | 东方财富股票数据 |\n| stock | 股票查询 |\n| stock-monitor | 股票监控 |\n| stock-board | 股票打板筛选 |\n| yanpan-finance | A 股多维量化分析 |\n| a-share-pro | A 股专业版 |\n\n需要我帮你安装其中某个吗？🦐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":2637,"output":168,"cacheRead":36685,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39490,"cost":{"input":0.0007911,"output":0.0002016,"cacheRead":0.0011005499999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0020932499999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773910480177}}
