{"type":"message","id":"fb028678","parentId":"cf5a9860","timestamp":"2026-03-19T09:01:15.746Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ibumjyrlm83a_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Fetching skill\n{\n  \"skill\": {\n    \"slug\": \"tushare-data\",\n    \"displayName\": \"Tushare Data\",\n    \"summary\": \"tushare是一个财经数据接口包，拥有丰富的数据内容，如股票、基金、期货、数字货币等行情数据，公司财务、基金经理等基本面数据。该模块通过标准化API方式统一了数据资产的对外服务方式，以帮助有需要的技术用户更实时、简洁、轻量的使用相关数据。\",\n    \"tags\": {\n      \"latest\": \"1.0.12\"\n    },\n    \"stats\": {\n      \"comments\": 0,\n      \"downloads\": 4627,\n      \"installsAllTime\": 52,\n      \"installsCurrent\": 51,\n      \"stars\": 19,\n      \"versions\": 12\n    },\n    \"createdAt\": 1772507593510,\n    \"updatedAt\": 1773896777722\n  },\n  \"latestVersion\": {\n    \"version\": \"1.0.12\",\n    \"createdAt\": 1773737923974,\n    \"changelog\": \"- Major update: Added extensive new reference documentation for ETF、债券、外汇、指数等专题的数据接口。\\n- 79 new files introduced, covering ETF实时行情、ETF份额规模、ETF基准指数、可转债信息、债券回购、外汇行情、指数成分与大盘等内容。\\n- 用户可以查阅详细的API参数与示例，快速理解各大类金融数据接口的使用方法。\\n- 推动了接口文档的结构化，提升查找和使用的便利性。\",\n    \"license\": \"MIT-0\"\n  },\n  \"owner\": {\n    \"handle\": \"lidayan\",\n    \"userId\": \"kn70zya1kw0k7m0ejsxm94f64x824jm4\",\n    \"displayName\": \"lidayan\",\n    \"image\": \"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16535491?v=4\"\n  },\n  \"version\": null,\n  \"versions\": null,\n  \"file\": null\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1592,"aggregated":"- Fetching skill\n{\n  \"skill\": {\n    \"slug\": \"tushare-data\",\n    \"displayName\": \"Tushare Data\",\n    \"summary\": \"tushare是一个财经数据接口包，拥有丰富的数据内容，如股票、基金、期货、数字货币等行情数据，公司财务、基金经理等基本面数据。该模块通过标准化API方式统一了数据资产的对外服务方式，以帮助有需要的技术用户更实时、简洁、轻量的使用相关数据。\",\n    \"tags\": {\n      \"latest\": \"1.0.12\"\n    },\n    \"stats\": {\n      \"comments\": 0,\n      \"downloads\": 4627,\n      \"installsAllTime\": 52,\n      \"installsCurrent\": 51,\n      \"stars\": 19,\n      \"versions\": 12\n    },\n    \"createdAt\": 1772507593510,\n    \"updatedAt\": 1773896777722\n  },\n  \"latestVersion\": {\n    \"version\": \"1.0.12\",\n    \"createdAt\": 1773737923974,\n    \"changelog\": \"- Major update: Added extensive new reference documentation for ETF、债券、外汇、指数等专题的数据接口。\\n- 79 new files introduced, covering ETF实时行情、ETF份额规模、ETF基准指数、可转债信息、债券回购、外汇行情、指数成分与大盘等内容。\\n- 用户可以查阅详细的API参数与示例，快速理解各大类金融数据接口的使用方法。\\n- 推动了接口文档的结构化，提升查找和使用的便利性。\",\n    \"license\": \"MIT-0\"\n  },\n  \"owner\": {\n    \"handle\": \"lidayan\",\n    \"userId\": \"kn70zya1kw0k7m0ejsxm94f64x824jm4\",\n    \"displayName\": \"lidayan\",\n    \"image\": \"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16535491?v=4\"\n  },\n  \"version\": null,\n  \"versions\": null,\n  \"file\": null\n}","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773910875743}}
{"type":"message","id":"c0864e1d","parentId":"fb028678","timestamp":"2026-03-19T09:01:15.827Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ibumjyrlm83a_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Fetching skill\n{\n  \"skill\": {\n    \"slug\": \"eastmoney-stock\",\n    \"displayName\": \"Eastmoney Stock\",\n    \"summary\": \"查询东方财富股票数据，包括个股行情、涨跌幅、成交量等。用于回答股票相关问题。\",\n    \"tags\": {\n      \"latest\": \"1.0.0\"\n    },\n    \"stats\": {\n      \"comments\": 0,\n      \"downloads\": 1120,\n      \"installsAllTime\": 6,\n      \"installsCurrent\": 6,\n      \"stars\": 1,\n      \"versions\": 1\n    },\n    \"createdAt\": 1772925042828,\n    \"updatedAt\": 1772925050619\n  },\n  \"latestVersion\": {\n    \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n    \"createdAt\": 1772925042828,\n    \"changelog\": \"Initial release of eastmoney-stock.\\n\\n- Query real-time stock data from Eastmoney, including price, change percentage, and volume.\\n- Supports A-shares, Hong Kong stocks (add .HK), and US stocks (add .N).\\n- Provides top gainers/losers and watchlist queries.\\n- Designed to answer natural language stock questions in Chinese.\\n- Data may be delayed by a few minutes.\",\n    \"license\": null\n  },\n  \"owner\": {\n    \"handle\": \"dongchun2008\",\n    \"userId\": \"kn74khgesz3jbf5751ak03my8n81jbe4\",\n    \"displayName\": \"dongchun2008\",\n    \"image\": \"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/106893657?v=4\"\n  },\n  \"version\": null,\n  \"versions\": null,\n  \"file\": null\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1668,"aggregated":"- Fetching skill\n{\n  \"skill\": {\n    \"slug\": \"eastmoney-stock\",\n    \"displayName\": \"Eastmoney Stock\",\n    \"summary\": \"查询东方财富股票数据，包括个股行情、涨跌幅、成交量等。用于回答股票相关问题。\",\n    \"tags\": {\n      \"latest\": \"1.0.0\"\n    },\n    \"stats\": {\n      \"comments\": 0,\n      \"downloads\": 1120,\n      \"installsAllTime\": 6,\n      \"installsCurrent\": 6,\n      \"stars\": 1,\n      \"versions\": 1\n    },\n    \"createdAt\": 1772925042828,\n    \"updatedAt\": 1772925050619\n  },\n  \"latestVersion\": {\n    \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n    \"createdAt\": 1772925042828,\n    \"changelog\": \"Initial release of eastmoney-stock.\\n\\n- Query real-time stock data from Eastmoney, including price, change percentage, and volume.\\n- Supports A-shares, Hong Kong stocks (add .HK), and US stocks (add .N).\\n- Provides top gainers/losers and watchlist queries.\\n- Designed to answer natural language stock questions in Chinese.\\n- Data may be delayed by a few minutes.\",\n    \"license\": null\n  },\n  \"owner\": {\n    \"handle\": \"dongchun2008\",\n    \"userId\": \"kn74khgesz3jbf5751ak03my8n81jbe4\",\n    \"displayName\": \"dongchun2008\",\n    \"image\": \"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/106893657?v=4\"\n  },\n  \"version\": null,\n  \"versions\": null,\n  \"file\": null\n}","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773910875825}}
{"type":"message","id":"5dec7334","parentId":"c0864e1d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T09:01:15.880Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ibumjyrlm83a_3","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Fetching skill\n{\n  \"skill\": {\n    \"slug\": \"stock\",\n    \"displayName\": \"股票查询\",\n    \"summary\": \"查询A股、港股、美股股票的实时行情，包括价格、涨跌幅、开盘价、成交量等详细数据。\",\n    \"tags\": {\n      \"latest\": \"1.0.0\"\n    },\n    \"stats\": {\n      \"comments\": 0,\n      \"downloads\": 812,\n      \"installsAllTime\": 18,\n      \"installsCurrent\": 18,\n      \"stars\": 0,\n      \"versions\": 1\n    },\n    \"createdAt\": 1772343297159,\n    \"updatedAt\": 1772343667087\n  },\n  \"latestVersion\": {\n    \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n    \"createdAt\": 1772343297159,\n    \"changelog\": \"Initial release of Stock Skill - 股票查询\\n\\n- Query real-time stock data for A-shares, Hong Kong stocks, and US stocks.\\n- Supports automatic market identification for A-shares (Shanghai/Shenzhen).\\n- Retrieves information using Sina Finance API.\\n- Outputs current price, change percentage and amount, open/high/low price, trading volume/value, and turnover rate.\",\n    \"license\": null\n  },\n  \"owner\": {\n    \"handle\": \"MrBlackerX\",\n    \"userId\": \"kn7exbcm6z1y1537p1sb68gq2x823195\",\n    \"displayName\": \"MrBlackerX\",\n    \"image\": \"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/46913471?v=4\"\n  },\n  \"version\": null,\n  \"versions\": null,\n  \"file\": null\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1716,"aggregated":"- Fetching skill\n{\n  \"skill\": {\n    \"slug\": \"stock\",\n    \"displayName\": \"股票查询\",\n    \"summary\": \"查询A股、港股、美股股票的实时行情，包括价格、涨跌幅、开盘价、成交量等详细数据。\",\n    \"tags\": {\n      \"latest\": \"1.0.0\"\n    },\n    \"stats\": {\n      \"comments\": 0,\n      \"downloads\": 812,\n      \"installsAllTime\": 18,\n      \"installsCurrent\": 18,\n      \"stars\": 0,\n      \"versions\": 1\n    },\n    \"createdAt\": 1772343297159,\n    \"updatedAt\": 1772343667087\n  },\n  \"latestVersion\": {\n    \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n    \"createdAt\": 1772343297159,\n    \"changelog\": \"Initial release of Stock Skill - 股票查询\\n\\n- Query real-time stock data for A-shares, Hong Kong stocks, and US stocks.\\n- Supports automatic market identification for A-shares (Shanghai/Shenzhen).\\n- Retrieves information using Sina Finance API.\\n- Outputs current price, change percentage and amount, open/high/low price, trading volume/value, and turnover rate.\",\n    \"license\": null\n  },\n  \"owner\": {\n    \"handle\": \"MrBlackerX\",\n    \"userId\": \"kn7exbcm6z1y1537p1sb68gq2x823195\",\n    \"displayName\": \"MrBlackerX\",\n    \"image\": \"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/46913471?v=4\"\n  },\n  \"version\": null,\n  \"versions\": null,\n  \"file\": null\n}","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773910875878}}
