{"type":"message","id":"0c90c3a1","parentId":"3a8940ae","timestamp":"2026-03-19T09:02:02.262Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8rs9l6wt25jl_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Fetching skill\n{\n  \"skill\": {\n    \"slug\": \"a-share-pro\",\n    \"displayName\": \"A Share Pro\",\n    \"summary\": \"A 股专业监控工具 - 轻量级自选股管理 + 多数据源实时行情。支持腾讯财经/雪球/百度/Tushare 自动切换，纯文本存储，无需数据库依赖。用于日常股票跟踪、自选股管理和投资组合监控。\",\n    \"tags\": {\n      \"latest\": \"1.0.0\"\n    },\n    \"stats\": {\n      \"comments\": 0,\n      \"downloads\": 1169,\n      \"installsAllTime\": 13,\n      \"installsCurrent\": 11,\n      \"stars\": 2,\n      \"versions\": 1\n    },\n    \"createdAt\": 1772785560798,\n    \"updatedAt\": 1772785577973\n  },\n  \"latestVersion\": {\n    \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n    \"createdAt\": 1772785560798,\n    \"changelog\": \"- 首发版本，功能完整，专为 A 股用户设计的自选股监控与管理工具\\n- 支持多数据源智能切换（腾讯财经/雪球/百度/Tushare），主要使用免费接口\\n- 纯文本本地存储，无需数据库，轻松安装与迁移\\n- 提供自选股添加、列表查看、行情汇总、持仓导出等基础功能\\n- 支持命令行批量操作及定时任务\\n- 配置灵活，便于自定义与拓展\",\n    \"license\": null\n  },\n  \"owner\": {\n    \"handle\": \"wran93409\",\n    \"userId\": \"kn75fcc6frf1s3g4j1czmkjc2d82bj4c\",\n    \"displayName\": \"wran93409\",\n    \"image\": \"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/49407965?v=4\"\n  },\n  \"version\": null,\n  \"versions\": null,\n  \"file\": null\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1599,"aggregated":"- Fetching skill\n{\n  \"skill\": {\n    \"slug\": \"a-share-pro\",\n    \"displayName\": \"A Share Pro\",\n    \"summary\": \"A 股专业监控工具 - 轻量级自选股管理 + 多数据源实时行情。支持腾讯财经/雪球/百度/Tushare 自动切换，纯文本存储，无需数据库依赖。用于日常股票跟踪、自选股管理和投资组合监控。\",\n    \"tags\": {\n      \"latest\": \"1.0.0\"\n    },\n    \"stats\": {\n      \"comments\": 0,\n      \"downloads\": 1169,\n      \"installsAllTime\": 13,\n      \"installsCurrent\": 11,\n      \"stars\": 2,\n      \"versions\": 1\n    },\n    \"createdAt\": 1772785560798,\n    \"updatedAt\": 1772785577973\n  },\n  \"latestVersion\": {\n    \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n    \"createdAt\": 1772785560798,\n    \"changelog\": \"- 首发版本，功能完整，专为 A 股用户设计的自选股监控与管理工具\\n- 支持多数据源智能切换（腾讯财经/雪球/百度/Tushare），主要使用免费接口\\n- 纯文本本地存储，无需数据库，轻松安装与迁移\\n- 提供自选股添加、列表查看、行情汇总、持仓导出等基础功能\\n- 支持命令行批量操作及定时任务\\n- 配置灵活，便于自定义与拓展\",\n    \"license\": null\n  },\n  \"owner\": {\n    \"handle\": \"wran93409\",\n    \"userId\": \"kn75fcc6frf1s3g4j1czmkjc2d82bj4c\",\n    \"displayName\": \"wran93409\",\n    \"image\": \"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/49407965?v=4\"\n  },\n  \"version\": null,\n  \"versions\": null,\n  \"file\": null\n}","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773910922259}}
{"type":"message","id":"7ee12d51","parentId":"0c90c3a1","timestamp":"2026-03-19T09:02:11.557Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great, now I have all the info. Let me present a nice table to Sir.","thinkingSignature":"550be3f78637f17ce5d46ba3d5f2cc493d46355990a3e1ffbb2cb376903c5b1e"},{"type":"text","text":"Sir，这是为您整理的国内金融类技能列表：\n\n| 技能 | 简介 | 下载量 | 版本 |\n|------|------|--------|------|\n| **tushare-data** | 财经数据接口霸主，支持股票、基金、期货、数字货币等行情及基本面数据 | 4,627 | 1.0.12 |\n| **stock-monitor** | 股票价格实时监控，支持多股监控、自定义涨跌阈值提醒 | 3,655 | 1.3.0 |\n| **eastmoney-stock** | 东方财富股票数据查询，支持A股、港股、美股 | 1,120 | 1.0.0 |\n| **a-share-pro** | A股专业监控，自选股管理+多数据源实时行情 | 1,169 | 1.0.0 |\n| **stock** | A股/港股/美股实时行情查询 | 812 | 1.0.0 |\n| **stock-board** | 股票打板筛选，涨停板、强势股、板块统计 | 483 | 1.0.0 |\n| **yanpan-finance** | A股多维量化分析，券商研报、AI新闻分析 | 209 | 1.5.0 |\n\n**💡 建议：**\n- 想要**全面数据** → tushare-data（最强王者）\n- 想要**价格监控提醒** → stock-monitor\n- 想要**打板/短线** → stock-board\n\n需要我帮您安装吗？🦐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":6678,"output":341,"cacheRead":36685,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43704,"cost":{"input":0.0020034,"output":0.00040919999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0011005499999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0035131499999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773910922262}}
