{"type":"message","id":"e1bf85a0","parentId":"34f3fc0c","timestamp":"2026-03-19T09:30:57.794Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"tushare-data 需要配置 Tushare Token。让我给 Sir 整理一个简单的使用说明。","thinkingSignature":"6befbc43a37f1a18bbde92a3c5808e2aa719faf708ceb035402e62a82f5bfb5e"},{"type":"text","text":"Sir，使用方法如下：\n\n## 🚀 使用方法\n\n### 1️⃣ tushare-data（需要配置 Token）\n\n**首次配置**：\n```\n1. 去 https://tushare.pro/register 注册账号\n2. 获取 Token\n3. 设置环境变量：TUSHARE_TOKEN=你的Token\n```\n\n**然后可以直接问我**，例如：\n- \"帮我查一下贵州茅台的股票\"\n- \"获取最近一周的基金净值\"\n- \"A股今日涨停板有哪些\"\n\n---\n\n### 2️⃣ 其他技能（直接可用）\n\n| 技能 | 用法 |\n|------|------|\n| **stock** | \"查一下招商银行股价\" |\n| **eastmoney-stock** | \"招商银行今天涨多少\" |\n| **stock-board** | \"今日涨停板有哪些\" |\n| **a-share-pro** | \"我的自选股有哪些\" |\n| **yanpan-finance** | \"帮我分析一下某只股票\" |\n\n---\n\n**⚠️ 重要**：tushare-data 需要您先去 [tushare.pro](https://tushare.pro/register) 注册获取 Token，配置好后才能使用完整功能。\n\n其他技能可以直接用，您想先试试哪个？🦐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":21661,"output":272,"cacheRead":36685,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58618,"cost":{"input":0.006498299999999999,"output":0.00032639999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0011005499999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00792525}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773912643849}}
