{"type":"message","id":"d1a2c40a","parentId":"ab6d3fbc","timestamp":"2026-03-19T09:31:53.732Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to try the other skills first, before configuring tushare. Let me show them how to use the other skills that don't need token configuration.","thinkingSignature":"d938346853f5a524b742a87a95448ec09b12bc67361f46be9e8e01f45ec1f34b"},{"type":"text","text":"好嘞！先玩其他的～\n\n**直接可用的技能**：\n\n| 技能 | 示例问题 |\n|------|----------|\n| **stock** | \"查一下招商银行股价\" / \"600036 现在多少\" |\n| **eastmoney-stock** | \"招商银行今天涨多少\" / \"给我看看今日涨幅榜\" |\n| **stock-board** | \"今日涨停板有哪些\" / \"帮我筛选一下打板股票\" |\n| **a-share-pro** | \"添加自选股 600036\" / \"查看我的自选股\" |\n| **yanpan-finance** | \"分析一下贵州茅台\" |\n\n您挑一个想问的吧！🦐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":64,"output":178,"cacheRead":45091,"cacheWrite":13698,"totalTokens":59031,"cost":{"input":0.0000192,"output":0.0002136,"cacheRead":0.00135273,"cacheWrite":0.0016437599999999998,"total":0.0032292899999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773912697283}}
