{"type":"message","id":"fa13df91","parentId":"b63a4600","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:34:47.998Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me compile a comprehensive list for Sir.","thinkingSignature":"3322e3668315c68e685dce62135df99d21be7134055d9f229e25707405a3f5d0"},{"type":"text","text":"Sir，给您整理更多金融类技能：\n\n---\n\n## 📈 股票/量化（国内可用）\n| 技能 | 描述 |\n|------|------|\n| **futures** | 期货查询 |\n| **stock-recommend** | 股票推荐（A股、港股、美股） |\n| **a-stock-fundamental-screening** | A股基本面筛选 |\n| **a-stock-premarket-briefing** | A股盘前简报 |\n| **stock-analyst** | 股票分析 |\n| **a-stock-market-sentiment** | A股市场情绪量化 |\n| **quant-trading-cn** | 量化交易CN |\n| **ac-stock-ultrashort** | A股超短线交易策略 |\n| **tradingagents-analysis** | Trading Agents 分析 |\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 交易工具\n| 技能 | 描述 |\n|------|------|\n| **eastmoney-trading** | 东方财富交易 |\n| **trading-coach** | 交易教练 |\n| **quant-trading-signals** | 量化交易信号 |\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 数据源\n| 技能 | 描述 |\n|------|------|\n| **akshare-zh** | Akshare（财经数据开源库） |\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 需翻墙（国内不稳）\n- crypto-trading-bot\n- binance-spot-trader\n- polymarket-openclaw-trader\n\n---\n\n想安装哪些？🦐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":34920,"output":316,"cacheRead":35271,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70507,"cost":{"input":0.010476,"output":0.0003792,"cacheRead":0.00105813,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01191333}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773934463906}}
