{"type":"message","id":"93b84674","parentId":"08a803c3","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:38:11.496Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_l99ak9g528p6_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: fundamental-screening\ndescription: 用财务指标快速排除垃圾股，找到有基本面支撑的标的。用于A股基本面选股。\n---\n\n# 基本面筛选 Skill\n\n## 核心能力\n\n用财务指标快速排除垃圾股，找到有基本面支撑的标的。\n\n## 筛选规则\n\n### 成长股筛选\n- 连续3年营收增速 ≥ 30%\n- 净利润增速 ≥ 25%\n- ROE ≥ 15%\n\n### 价值股筛选\n- 市盈率（PE）< 行业均值\n\n[31 more lines in file. Use offset=21 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773934691494}}
