{"type":"message","id":"27d49a2c","parentId":"4092b7a0","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:59:01.660Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if there are alternative search engines they can use instead of Brave API. Let me check what other search options are available. The skill description mentioned multi-search-engine has 17 search engines. Let me check if we can configure that differently or use other approaches.","thinkingSignature":"44be5818ceb78eeadce76eba34352367985983bc46d093fa51fc82f2a0ed789f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qbmh1jzx131x_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multi-search-engine/SKILL.md","limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":147,"output":105,"cacheRead":86766,"cacheWrite":302,"totalTokens":87320,"cost":{"input":0.0000441,"output":0.000126,"cacheRead":0.00260298,"cacheWrite":0.00003624,"total":0.0028093199999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773935933228}}
{"type":"message","id":"08f04559","parentId":"27d49a2c","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:59:01.668Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qbmh1jzx131x_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: \"multi-search-engine\"\r\ndescription: \"Multi search engine integration with 17 engines (8 CN + 9 Global). Supports advanced search operators, time filters, site search, privacy engines, and WolframAlpha knowledge queries. No API keys required.\"\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Multi Search Engine v2.0.1\r\n\r\nIntegration of 17 search engines for web crawling without API keys.\r\n\r\n## Search Engines\r\n\r\n### Domestic (8)\r\n- **Baidu**: `https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}`\r\n- **Bing CN**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=0`\r\n- **Bing INT**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=1`\r\n- **360**: `https://www.so.com/s?q={keyword}`\r\n- **Sogou**: `https://sogou.com/web?query={keyword}`\r\n- **WeChat**: `https://wx.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&query={keyword}`\r\n- **Toutiao**: `https://so.toutiao.com/search?keyword={keyword}`\r\n- **Jisilu**: `https://www.jisilu.cn/explore/?keyword={keyword}`\r\n\r\n### International (9)\r\n- **Google**: `https://www.google.com/search?q={keyword}`\r\n- **Google HK**: `https://www.google.com.hk/search?q={keyword}`\r\n- **DuckDuckGo**: `https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q={keyword}`\r\n- **Yahoo**: `https://search.yahoo.com/search?p={keyword}`\r\n- **Startpage**: `https://www.startpage.com/sp/search?query={keyword}`\r\n- **Brave**: `https://search.brave.com/search?q={keyword}`\r\n- **Ecosia**: `https://www.ecosia.org/search?q={keyword}`\r\n- **Qwant**: `https://www.qwant.com/?q={keyword}`\r\n- **WolframAlpha**: `https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i={keyword}`\r\n\r\n## Quick Examples\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\n// Basic search\r\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=python+tutorial\"})\r\n\r\n// Site-specific\r\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=site:github.com+react\"})\r\n\r\n// File type\r\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=machine+learning+filetype:pdf\"})\r\n\r\n// Time filter (past week)\r\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=ai+news&tbs=qdr:w\"})\r\n\r\n// Privacy search\r\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=privacy+tools\"})\r\n\r\n\n[61 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773935941666}}
{"type":"message","id":"cabb86d5","parentId":"08f04559","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:59:08.205Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good news! The multi-search-engine skill doesn't require API keys - it uses direct web scraping from various search engines. Let me tell the user they can use this instead.","thinkingSignature":"58b0a4d12691f44f91bbe886e9581d88914f949b4e3baebedf0c6fd0296555b6"},{"type":"text","text":"Sir好消息！**不需要 API Key！** 🎉\n\n这个 `multi-search-engine` 技能内置了 **17 个搜索引擎**，直接抓取网页，**不需要任何 API**！\n\n---\n\n### ✅ 可用的搜索引擎\n\n**国内（8个）**：\n- 百度、Bing中国、360搜索、搜狗\n- 微信搜索、头条搜索、雪球（Jisilu）\n\n**国际（9个）**：\n- Google、DuckDuckGo、Yahoo\n- Startpage、Brave、Ecosia、Qwant\n- WolframAlpha（知识问答）\n\n---\n\n所以盘前简报**可以直接用**！让我测试一下：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ykbtknv8oc2t_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"import requests; r = requests.get('https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=A股+今日+市场', headers={'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0'}); print('OK' if r.status_code==200 else 'FAIL', len(r.text))\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":52659,"output":258,"cacheRead":35271,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88188,"cost":{"input":0.015797699999999998,"output":0.0003096,"cacheRead":0.00105813,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01716543}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773935941669}}
